  "texts": [
    "These approaches support sustainable operations while attenuating grid demand [162].",
    "These smart and efficient cooling strategies underscore a shift towards multi-dimensional optimization to balance energy, water, carbon, and operational complexity.C.",
    "Solutions on AI End-User Side 1) Energy-Aware Prompting and AI Model Selection: Endusers and developers of AI applications can contribute to reducing the AI electricity footprint through energy-aware application development and informed usage decisions.",
    "For endusers, one critical approach is the adoption of energy-efficient prompting strategies and the selection of appropriately scaled models.",
    "Recent studies have shown that longer, more verbose prompts, while potentially improving model interpretability or output alignment, can significantly increase the number of tokens to be processed and thus greatly elevate the power consumption of LLMs [163]- [165]."
